Dougal Williams | Partner, Investment Advisor in Portland, OR



Dougal Williams | Partner, Investment Advisor in Portland, OR









































 



















Select Page


  
 
 







    
Dougal WilliamsChief Investment Officer, PartnerOnce a world-ranked tennis player, Dougal’s approach to each match was simple: develop a solid game plan and try his best to execute it. This is a mindset that helps at the office, too.
As our Chief Investment Officer, Dougal is responsible for orchestrating and implementing the firm’s investment and wealth management research. In addition to developing close relationships with clients, this daily opportunity to learn and help teach others is what he enjoys most about his job.
One of the most energetic folks in the office, Dougal can be found trail running or on the tennis court, undoubtedly taking instruction from one of his three young daughters.
